## UiSystem-A3 Theme & Accent System Architecture
**Status:** approved
**Tags:** stack:frontend

```mermaid
graph LR
    T[useTheme.ts] -->|localStorage| LS[vitepress-theme-appearance]
    T -->|toggle| HTML[<html class="dark|light">]
    A[useAccentColor.ts] -->|CSS vars| ROOT[:root]
    ROOT -->|tailwind dark:| UI[All Vue components]
```

| Concern | Decision |
|---------|----------|
| Theme persistence | localStorage key `vitepress-theme-appearance` for compatibility |
| Accent application | CSS custom properties (`--color-primary-500`, etc.) injected at runtime |
| System preference | `matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)')` with live listener |

- No server involvement; purely client-side state
- Both composables are singletons (module-level refs)

